---
title: Beef Flank & Truffle Mushroom Sauce with Parmesan Cos Salad & Garlic Butter Potatoes
description: Make your holiday dinner merry and bright with a juicy steak dinner! Tender beef meets a rich, velvety mushroom sauce that’s
sure to bring some extra cheer. Pair it with a nutty Parmesan salad for a crisp touch and warm, golden potatoes for a holiday
feast that’s as comforting as a cosy Christmas night!
